FIX:     After any HexCard.tsx edit, grep for "}\n  const S=1024" pattern
WEIGHT:  check_orphan_after_hexcard_edit = 1.0

PATTERN: lazy import missing in App.tsx
CAUSED:  AdminPanel is not defined at runtime
FIX:     Check existing lazy imports before adding new component to routes
WEIGHT:  verify_lazy_import_before_route = 1.0

PATTERN: JSX provider opened but not closed
CAUSED:  Unterminated JSX in App.tsx (WalletProvider)
FIX:     Count opening/closing tags after wrapping in providers
WEIGHT:  count_jsx_tags_after_provider_wrap = 1.0

PATTERN: django_migrations has entries for deleted files
CAUSED:  InconsistentMigrationHistory on every migrate
FIX:     DELETE FROM django_migrations WHERE app NOT IN (safe_apps) then fake-initial
WEIGHT:  clean_migrations_table_before_migrate = 1.0

PATTERN: whitenoise in MIDDLEWARE but not installed in venv
CAUSED:  ModuleNotFoundError on every request
FIX:     Remove from INSTALLED_APPS + MIDDLEWARE both
WEIGHT:  check_installed_before_middleware = 1.0

PATTERN: token_blacklist still referenced after removal
CAUSED:  OperationalError on login (missing table)
FIX:     Remove from INSTALLED_APPS + clean django_migrations table
WEIGHT:  full_removal_requires_settings_and_db = 1.0

PATTERN: Vite /assets/*.js served as text/html
CAUSED:  MIME type error, app completely broken
FIX:     Add /assets/ exclusion in catchall + static_serve route
WEIGHT:  vite_assets_need_explicit_django_route = 1.0

PATTERN: API returns object, .map() called on it
CAUSED:  TypeError: s.map is not a function
FIX:     Array.isArray(data) ? data : (data?.results ?? [])
WEIGHT:  always_guard_api_data_before_map = 1.0

PATTERN: raw PAT in committed file
CAUSED:  GitHub push protection rejects push
FIX:     Never store raw tokens in files. Use <PAT> placeholder.
         Store token only in git remote URL (not committed).
WEIGHT:  never_commit_raw_token = 1.0

PATTERN: squash reset picks up stale file from repo (not local)
CAUSED:  brain files appear empty after force push
FIX:     After reset --soft, verify file content before committing
WEIGHT:  verify_file_content_after_reset = 1.0

